{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Who was a partisan and he was arrested as such.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not as a Jew, but he was arrested as in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't ask me why they didn't kill him right away, but they sent him to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he arrived to the camps probably in about 19-- either it was at the end-- in the beginning of '44, or sometime during 1944.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we have kind of adopted him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We already, as I've indicated before, I was singing in a choir.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had an extra bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had the bread from that civilian guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I could-- we helped him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was my brother's age, and my brother was 11 years older than I am.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And kind of took a liking to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I believed that this man, at one time, was telling us a story that he came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But he was smuggled in on a boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And of course, he was repatriated, and he had to go back in that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we kind of took a liking to him, and he took a liking to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we helped him out with a little extra soup, a little extra bread in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he arrived in Buchenwald with us together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he arrived in there, Buchenwald had a tremendous underground movement in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The guys-- there were quite a few-- commanders from the underground, which were in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I do have certain documents from these commanders who have given me witnesses, I guess.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I finally left Belgium, I had to have some papers for the government to show them that I was on my best behavior in the camps.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, if I could behave otherwise in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
